query: DELETE FROM properties WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT p1.id FROM properties p1 WHERE p1.parcelId IS NOT NULL AND p1.parcelId != '' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM properties p2 WHERE p2.county = p1.county AND p2.parcelId = p1.parcelId AND p2.id < p1.id)) AS duplicates_to_delete)
